{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"9":{"eng-name":"Zakat (Kitab Al-Zakat)","ara-name":"كتاب الزكاة"}},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1556,"hadithnumber_last":1700,"arabicnumber_first":1556,"arabicnumber_last":1700}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1652,"arabicnumber":1652,"text":"حدثنا نصر بن علي، اخبرنا ابي، عن خالد بن قيس، عن قتادة، عن انس، ان النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم وجد تمرة فقال \" لولا اني اخاف ان تكون صدقة لاكلتها \" . قال ابو داود رواه هشام عن قتادة هكذا","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (2055) Sahih Muslim (1071)"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":97},"chapter":{"id":30,"ara-name":"باب الصَّدَقَةِ عَلَى بَنِي هَاشِمٍ","eng-name":"On Giving Sadaqah To Banu Hashim","isFirstHadith":false}}]}